47:41.661 --> 47:44.080
- Has he eaten?
- I don't know, sir.

47:44.664 --> 47:48.043
- Go get him some clothes.
- Yes, General.

47:51.338 --> 47:55.009
Your Honor, this is a man who heads
a large criminal organization...

47:55.134 --> 47:59.513
with international contacts
we can only begin to understand.

47:59.638 --> 48:02.183
Our case against him is very strong.

48:02.308 --> 48:06.854
He is not a flight risk.
His flight is assured.

48:06.979 --> 48:10.858
The people ask that Your Honor
deny bail. Thank you.

48:12.151 --> 48:14.195
My client is no more
a flight risk...

48:14.320 --> 48:16.447
than Your Honor
or the able prosecutor.

48:16.530 --> 48:18.532
He's a pillar
of his community;

48:18.657 --> 48:22.536
a family man with a wife and child
living in La Jolla,

48:22.620 --> 48:25.122
the communitywhere he has made
his home for the past 20 years.

48:25.206 --> 48:27.124
As our defense
will quickly show,

48:27.208 --> 48:29.126
my client is guilty
of nothing more...

48:29.210 --> 48:32.129
than being the handy target
of an admitted criminal.

48:32.213 --> 48:35.591
Therefore, we ask that you release
Carl Ayala on his own recognizance.

48:37.176 --> 48:39.053
I'm going to deny bail.

49:10.585 --> 49:13.422
I appreciate you coming in
so early this morning.

49:13.547 --> 49:15.757
Judge Wakefield,
it's an honor to handle it.

49:15.882 --> 49:18.927
She's a minor. It probably would have
expunged on her 18th birthday anyway.

49:19.052 --> 49:23.932
