01:00:58.015 --> 01:01:00.101
Man, I love this place.

01:01:23.666 --> 01:01:27.461
I wish we could
just stay here.

01:01:27.545 --> 01:01:31.507
Just be here forever
and ever and...

01:01:31.590 --> 01:01:34.218
make a little home here.

