01:02:45.166 --> 01:02:47.877
Lost my virginity,
was a sophomore in high school.

01:02:47.960 --> 01:02:50.338
- That's cool.
- Yeah, it was sweet.

01:02:51.547 --> 01:02:53.424
Did he treat you good?

01:03:09.065 --> 01:03:11.442
- Who's this guy?
- I don't know.

01:03:11.526 --> 01:03:13.778
- I never seen him before.
- He's going right for the kid.

01:03:18.282 --> 01:03:20.159
David!

01:03:22.203 --> 01:03:24.622
David, come back here!

01:03:26.791 --> 01:03:28.709
- Mom, Mom.
- Please, put down my son.

01:03:28.793 --> 01:03:31.213
Shouldn't let
your kid wander off with strangers.

01:03:31.296 --> 01:03:35.175
Karen, if he tries to move
with that kid, you break cover.

01:03:35.300 --> 01:03:39.763
Mrs. Ayala, your husband owes
a lot of money. Snapping this
kid's neck wouldn't cover it.

01:03:39.888 --> 01:03:42.808
You better come up with it in a hurry
or your kid is gonna disappear,

01:03:42.891 --> 01:03:45.519
and he won't turn up
until the evening news.

01:03:45.644 --> 01:03:49.148
You get only one warning.
First payment is $3 million.

01:04:13.839 --> 01:04:17.885
-Javier.
- Yes?

01:04:20.137 --> 01:04:21.805
What's up, Ana?

01:04:23.641 --> 01:04:26.603
Manolo never came home last night.

01:04:27.228 --> 01:04:29.606
Come in, come in. Sit down.

01:04:35.028 --> 01:04:37.363
I don't know where he is.

01:04:38.198 --> 01:04:40.033
He wasn't with you last night?

01:04:40.116 --> 01:04:42.035
No.

01:04:45.497 --> 01:04:47.165
I'm worried.

01:04:47.248 --> 01:04:49.959
Don't worry too much.
It makes you ugly.

01:04:50.251 --> 01:04:53.421
Do you want a coffee?
Coffee with sugar?

01:04:53.630 --> 01:04:55.548
- No.
- No?

01:04:56.925 --> 01:04:59.302
Look, Javier.

01:05:00.595 --> 01:05:02.931
I was going through his clothes
the other day.

01:05:04.933 --> 01:05:07.143
Look what I found.

01:05:10.522 --> 01:05:12.273
What is it?

01:05:19.156 --> 01:05:23.452
- What were you doing?
- I was with friends from work.

01:05:24.829 --> 01:05:27.623
Was Salazar there?

01:05:28.833 --> 01:05:31.252
No.

01:05:31.335 --> 01:05:33.963
The general is going
to Mexico City next week...

01:05:34.088 --> 01:05:36.298
and I'm not going
to get left behind.

01:06:01.407 --> 01:06:03.117
Javier Rodriguez.

01:06:03.242 --> 01:06:06.412
The word is you're not
that happy in your work.

01:06:06.579 --> 01:06:09.332
Maybe we can help.

01:06:27.726 --> 01:06:30.771
-John, how are you?
