01:07:25.910 --> 01:07:28.496
So, you're saying, actually,
that even a country of our size...

01:07:28.621 --> 01:07:32.333
and the budget that we throw
towards this issue,

01:07:32.458 --> 01:07:35.628
- they can compete at the same level?
