01:09:00.924 --> 01:09:04.594
When Carlos Ayala hires Michael Adler
as his legal defense,

01:09:04.719 --> 01:09:07.764
I send Ben Williams
down to San Diego as a prosecutor.

01:09:07.889 --> 01:09:10.809
Why? Because it's a symbol.

01:09:10.892 --> 01:09:14.104
It's a symbol that
we are sending the best.

01:09:14.187 --> 01:09:18.733
It's a message that we're
going after their top guys.

01:09:18.817 --> 01:09:21.319
So...

01:09:21.403 --> 01:09:23.446
right now...

01:09:23.571 --> 01:09:27.117
on this flight only...

01:09:27.242 --> 01:09:29.661
the dam is open...

01:09:29.743 --> 01:09:32.956
for new ideas.

01:09:43.091 --> 01:09:45.803
On a clear day,
you can see Mexico City.

01:09:45.928 --> 01:09:49.473
I have this place swept twice a day,
so just feel free to talk.

01:09:49.598 --> 01:09:53.519
I learned that back
in Miami in '85.

01:09:53.602 --> 01:09:55.646
U.S. shut down
the entire Caribbean.

01:09:55.771 --> 01:10:00.067
- It's a big game of whack-a-mole.
You knock it down in Miami--
- Arnie, I need money.

01:10:00.192 --> 01:10:03.487
Somebody-- I think it was the Obregons--
threatened David.

01:10:03.571 --> 01:10:06.866
They want a first payment
of $3 million.

01:10:06.949 --> 01:10:10.161
Oh, Helena.

01:10:10.286 --> 01:10:13.664
I'd give it to you myself, but I-I-I
just don't have that kind of money.

01:10:13.748 --> 01:10:15.666
Please. Does anyone owe us money?

01:10:15.750 --> 01:10:20.337
Yes, there are people that do owe
you money, but nobody's gonna pay.

01:10:20.463 --> 01:10:23.299
Carl's got too much heat on him.

01:10:23.382 --> 01:10:27.511
What about our other businesses,
our legitimate businesses?

01:10:27.636 --> 01:10:31.558
- Don't we own a construction--
