01:10:31.641 --> 01:10:33.852
Just tell me something
positive, Arnie.

01:10:33.977 --> 01:10:36.688
Give me some good news,
for Christ's sake.

01:10:36.772 --> 01:10:38.732
I'm sorry.

01:10:43.695 --> 01:10:46.698
I just keep wondering what's
gonna happen if he doesn't get out.

01:10:46.823 --> 01:10:50.285
Just never been
on my own before.

01:10:50.410 --> 01:10:54.039
Always had someone. Always.

01:11:01.588 --> 01:11:06.551
I remember the first time
that I saw you--

01:11:06.676 --> 01:11:11.598
little Helen Watts
from the wrong side of somewhere.

01:11:11.723 --> 01:11:17.521
Somehow I knew even then that your
survival skills were pretty well honed.

01:11:17.604 --> 01:11:21.233
Glad you think so, Arnie.

01:11:21.316 --> 01:11:26.030
I just keep picturing a debt-ridden,
30-year-old mother of two...

01:11:26.114 --> 01:11:30.243
whose ex-husband
is being compared to Pablo Escobar.

01:11:32.161 --> 01:11:36.249
I don't know anyone who wants
to be with someone like that.

01:11:38.793 --> 01:11:39.585
Do you?

01:11:39.877 --> 01:11:40.670
Do you?

01:12:14.412 --> 01:12:17.040
You two don't like me, do you?

01:12:17.499 --> 01:12:21.754
Miss, with all due respect,
we don't have an opinion.

01:12:21.837 --> 01:12:23.964
Maybe it's because
I'm going to have...

01:12:24.089 --> 01:12:26.133
the nicest home you've ever seen
in your miserable lives.

01:12:28.343 --> 01:12:30.888
The old man actually
kept his promise.

01:12:31.013 --> 01:12:35.309
The general is a man of his word.

01:12:36.894 --> 01:12:40.189
They will say anything
to get what they want...

01:12:40.314 --> 01:12:45.486
and then it's always
tomorrow, tomorrow, tomorrow.

01:12:45.569 --> 01:12:48.781
Occupational hazard, I guess.

01:13:12.555 --> 01:13:14.974
- The bags?

01:13:15.975 --> 01:13:22.524
-My love, it's beautiful! How beautiful!

01:13:22.649 --> 01:13:25.026
How are you feeling? Good?

01:13:26.444 --> 01:13:28.780
How handsome you are.

01:13:38.415 --> 01:13:40.041
Listen...

01:13:40.166 --> 01:13:42.544
the Scorpion is alive.

01:13:44.754 --> 01:13:46.506
Get in.

01:13:50.468 --> 01:13:53.930
Porfirio Madrigal
isn't dead after all!

01:13:54.681 --> 01:13:58.393
That means that Salazar is working
for the Juárez cartel.

01:13:59.769 --> 01:14:02.773
I can't believe
this doesn't matter to you.

01:14:04.024 --> 01:14:06.068
This is nothing new, Manolo.

01:14:06.193 --> 01:14:09.697
That's why Salazar is so interested
in cleaning up Tijuana.

01:14:09.780 --> 01:14:12.450
And he has plans for Juan Obregón,
the bastard.

01:14:13.701 --> 01:14:15.703
That's right.

01:14:17.413 --> 01:14:20.916
You know how much money
he would pay for this information?

01:14:21.000 --> 01:14:24.003
- How much?
- A fuckload of money, partner.

01:14:28.716 --> 01:14:33.262
- What's up, man?
- Take off your glasses.

01:14:33.387 --> 01:14:36.557
Take off your glasses
so I can see your eyes.

01:14:45.691 --> 01:14:49.612
We're going to keep
our mouths shut.

01:14:52.531 --> 01:14:54.618
Okay.

01:15:02.084 --> 01:15:05.128
I think we
may have found our Mexican drug czar.

01:15:05.253 --> 01:15:08.173
General Salazar.

01:15:08.256 --> 01:15:10.801
Be nice to have somebody
to workwith down there.

01:15:12.094 --> 01:15:15.305
Does this mean you're
gonna be gone more?

01:15:15.430 --> 01:15:17.641
Possibly, yeah.

01:15:19.851 --> 01:15:23.814
You might want to pencil in
a little face time with your daughter.

01:15:23.939 --> 01:15:26.650
- Barbara--
- Because I'm at the edge
of my capabilities, Robert.

01:15:26.775 --> 01:15:29.945
I think it's important
we maintain a unified front.

01:15:30.028 --> 01:15:32.155
If you start in
on the war metaphors,

01:15:32.239 --> 01:15:34.324
I'm gonna drive this car
into a telephone pole.

01:15:34.449 --> 01:15:37.994
- I am as worried as you are.
- Oh, I don't think so.

01:15:38.120 --> 01:15:40.038
"Leave me alone.
Give me some money."

01:15:40.122 --> 01:15:42.499
That's what I get
from our daughter.

01:15:42.582 --> 01:15:46.129
She has a way of shutting me out
that seems very familiar.

01:15:46.212 --> 01:15:51.175
Well, she has a way of self-medicating
that I'm sure is very familiar to you.

01:15:53.553 --> 01:15:55.555
I'm not the one who has
to have three scotches...

01:15:55.638 --> 01:15:57.557
just to walk in the house
and say hello.

01:15:57.640 --> 01:16:00.852
I have one drink before dinner
to take the edge off. It's different.

01:16:00.977 --> 01:16:05.189
-Oh, is it?
-Otherwise, I would be dying of boredom.

01:16:21.914 --> 01:16:25.752
Why don't you go in and tell
your daughter how bored you are?

01:17:22.226 --> 01:17:25.437
Caroline, open this door immediately.

01:17:25.562 --> 01:17:28.732
Who is it?
I'm going to the bathroom.

01:17:28.816 --> 01:17:31.194
- Open the goddamn door!
- One minute.

01:17:38.243 --> 01:17:40.453
Excuse me.
I have to go to bed.

01:17:43.665 --> 01:17:46.209
Oh, Jesus.

01:17:51.256 --> 01:17:53.675
You are not going anywhere, young lady.

01:17:53.758 --> 01:17:56.970
You stay right there.

01:18:02.725 --> 01:18:04.686
Where are they?

01:18:05.937 --> 01:18:07.856
Where the hell are the drugs?

01:18:07.939 --> 01:18:09.983
Where are they?

01:18:10.108 --> 01:18:12.026
Fuck you.

01:18:12.152 --> 01:18:14.112
Fuck you.

01:18:14.195 --> 01:18:18.324
I wasn't doing anything.
You're like the Gestapo.

01:18:18.450 --> 01:18:22.872
Fuck me. Fuck me.
Well, fuck you!

01:19:12.421 --> 01:19:14.632
- Javier, good to see you.
- How you doing, partner?

01:19:14.757 --> 01:19:17.886
Did you take the precautions
we discussed about being followed?

01:19:18.011 --> 01:19:20.222
- Yes, of course.
- Will you move to the middle, please?

01:19:20.347 --> 01:19:22.265
- You're not carrying a weapon?
- No.

01:19:22.349 --> 01:19:24.768
- Of course not.
- Where are you taking me?

01:19:24.851 --> 01:19:27.771
- Somewhere safe.
- Where?

01:19:27.854 --> 01:19:30.565
A place we have that we know
is protected. He's good. Let's go.

01:19:30.649 --> 01:19:32.859
- No, no. No, no, no.
- Don't worry. It's really safe.

01:19:32.943 --> 01:19:35.654
No, no, no, no, no.
This is safe. This is safe.

01:19:35.779 --> 01:19:38.240
Come on, Javier, close the door.
Everything is cool, all right?

01:19:38.365 --> 01:19:41.076
- This is safe.
- Come on.

01:19:41.201 --> 01:19:43.620
Allright.

01:19:43.703 --> 01:19:46.248
Where would you like to go?

01:19:46.331 --> 01:19:49.668
- Huh?
- Where do you want to go, Javier?

01:19:58.635 --> 01:20:03.348
I believe it's
important that we work together.

01:20:03.473 --> 01:20:07.102
Mexico and the United States.
One hand washing the other.

01:20:07.227 --> 01:20:10.106
We agree.

01:20:10.189 --> 01:20:13.192
So, maybe you can tell me
about your informants in our operations.

01:20:15.945 --> 01:20:19.449
We thought that maybe you'd have
that kind of information for us.

01:20:20.908 --> 01:20:24.954
This is a very different
proposition, my friend.

01:20:25.079 --> 01:20:28.124
We pay for that kind
of information.

01:20:28.249 --> 01:20:31.794
Is that what
you're talking about, Javier?

01:20:31.878 --> 01:20:33.963
Getting paid?

01:20:37.425 --> 01:20:39.385
You like baseball?

01:20:42.180 --> 01:20:47.643
We need lights for the parks
so kids can play at night.

01:20:48.936 --> 01:20:51.355
So it's safe.

01:20:51.439 --> 01:20:54.442
So they can play baseball.

01:20:54.525 --> 01:20:57.528
So they no become--

01:20:57.612 --> 01:20:59.530
Everybody like baseball.

01:20:59.614 --> 01:21:02.618
Everybody likes parks.

01:21:02.701 --> 01:21:06.080
Listen.

01:21:06.205 --> 01:21:10.167
I believe it's important that
the United State take an interest...

01:21:10.250 --> 01:21:12.336
in Tijuana now.

01:21:14.463 --> 01:21:17.925
That's what I'm talking about,
my friends.

01:21:18.467 --> 01:21:20.511
Accountnumber...

01:21:20.636 --> 01:21:25.682
8201-4302-8091...

01:21:25.808 --> 01:21:28.018
2431.

01:21:29.812 --> 01:21:31.855
A cash advance.

01:21:37.820 --> 01:21:40.405
How much can I get?

01:21:42.866 --> 01:21:44.785
That's it?

01:21:48.789 --> 01:21:50.874
You ever try the patch, man?

01:21:50.999 --> 01:21:52.919
- The what?
- The patch.

01:21:53.002 --> 01:21:56.714
- That shit doesn't work, bro.
- It worked for my cousin.

01:21:56.840 --> 01:21:59.717
- No shit?
- Yeah.

01:21:59.801 --> 01:22:02.387
He had to wear five or six
at a time, but it worked.

01:22:02.512 --> 01:22:04.931
- So, how's he doing now?
- Oh, he's dead.

01:22:06.391 --> 01:22:09.519
- He's dead?
- It wasn't from the patch, man.

01:22:09.602 --> 01:22:12.230
- Okay, she's coming out.
- On it.

01:22:12.355 --> 01:22:15.275
- What did he die from?
- His wife shot him.

01:22:15.358 --> 01:22:18.987
She's leaving her property.

01:22:19.112 --> 01:22:20.905
Where the hell is she going?

01:22:21.197 --> 01:22:23.116
Maybe her neighbors.

01:22:23.199 --> 01:22:26.411
No, I don't think the neighbors
are fucking with her too much
right about now.

01:22:26.536 --> 01:22:29.080
What does she have
in her hand there?

01:22:30.540 --> 01:22:35.086
She seems to be headed for the van.

01:22:40.550 --> 01:22:42.469
Oh, shit.

01:22:42.552 --> 01:22:46.599
- What-- Wh-What do we do?
- I-l don't know. What do we do?

01:22:46.682 --> 01:22:48.559
- What do you think she wants, man?
- She's your girlfriend.

01:22:48.642 --> 01:22:50.644
You think she'll invite you
to her baby shower?

01:22:50.728 --> 01:22:52.646
-Just say hello. Work it.
- All right, all right, all right.

01:22:52.730 --> 01:22:54.940
She's waiting outside the van.

01:22:55.065 --> 01:22:57.610
- Hello?
- Would you like some lemonade?

01:22:57.735 --> 01:23:01.781
- I was just making some.
- You want some lemonade?

01:23:01.906 --> 01:23:03.824
Sure.

01:23:03.908 --> 01:23:08.120
I knowt his is a difficult situation,
and you're only doing your jobs.

01:23:08.245 --> 01:23:11.665
I don't wish you guys
any ill will or anything like that.

01:23:11.749 --> 01:23:13.876
But I have a favor to ask you.

01:23:14.001 --> 01:23:16.128
You're asking us for a favor?

01:23:16.253 --> 01:23:18.464
Some man threatened my child.

01:23:18.589 --> 01:23:20.508
These charges have created
so much attention,

01:23:20.591 --> 01:23:24.637
it seems to be bringing
all the nutjobs out of the nutjar.

01:23:24.762 --> 01:23:27.681
Would you keep an eye out
for anything out of the ordinary?

01:23:28.849 --> 01:23:31.185
- Sure.
- Yeah, of course we will.

01:23:31.268 --> 01:23:33.813
- I'd really appreciate it.
- Sure.

01:23:33.938 --> 01:23:36.524
- Thanks.
- Thank you for the lemonade.

01:23:36.649 --> 01:23:39.027
You're welcome.

01:23:45.617 --> 01:23:49.037
I'm gonna get this analyzed
right away, bro.

01:23:51.873 --> 01:23:54.876
So, it was my birthday...

01:23:55.001 --> 01:23:57.879
and my ex-wife
was getting remarried...

01:23:57.963 --> 01:24:00.882
and I was in some church basement
telling a bunch of strangers...

01:24:00.966 --> 01:24:02.926
it was a good day because...

01:24:03.051 --> 01:24:05.387
I didn't have to eat
out of a Dumpster.

01:24:06.805 --> 01:24:09.724
That was enough to send me
out on a pretty big one.

01:24:09.808 --> 01:24:13.228
I've been thinking a lot
about the first step--

01:24:13.311 --> 01:24:17.023
that I came to believe
I was powerless over alcohol...

01:24:17.149 --> 01:24:19.192
and that my life
had become unmanageable.

01:24:19.317 --> 01:24:22.737
My disease tells me
that I don't have a disease,

01:24:22.821 --> 01:24:25.365
that it's my birthday
and I can have one little beer,

01:24:25.490 --> 01:24:29.202
one little line,
a little Valium.

01:24:29.327 --> 01:24:33.875
Six months later, I wake up
in a sober-living house in Philly.

01:24:34.000 --> 01:24:36.544
I'm from Dallas, people.

01:24:36.669 --> 01:24:40.214
It's a disease,
an allergy of the body,

01:24:40.339 --> 01:24:42.759
an obsession of the mind.

01:24:42.842 --> 01:24:45.052
So, my name is Marty,

01:24:45.178 --> 01:24:49.223
and today I'm a grateful,
recovering alcoholic.

01:24:49.348 --> 01:24:54.395
And it's a good day because I
didn't have to eat out of a Dumpster.

01:24:54.520 --> 01:24:56.439
Thanks.

01:24:58.858 --> 01:25:01.068
Hi.

01:25:02.528 --> 01:25:07.074
I'm Caroline.
I'm not sure I'm an alcoholic.

01:25:07.200 --> 01:25:11.746
I mean...
I don't really like to drink.

01:25:13.539 --> 01:25:18.586
For someone my age, it's a lot easier
to get drugs than it is to get alcohol.

01:25:23.217 --> 01:25:26.637
I guess I'm angry.

01:25:30.057 --> 01:25:33.602
I mean, I think I'm really angry
about a lot of stuff.

01:25:33.727 --> 01:25:37.648
I'm just... not sure what.

01:26:24.863 --> 01:26:27.198
Listen to me.
I built our house...

01:26:27.282 --> 01:26:29.451
and I'm not gonna lose it.

01:26:32.370 --> 01:26:34.247
My business--

01:26:34.372 --> 01:26:39.711
that would take a lot
of private study.

01:26:45.508 --> 01:26:49.512
I suggest...
you look into the Coronel.

01:26:49.596 --> 01:26:54.350
- The painting?
- Into selling it.

01:26:54.476 --> 01:26:56.603
If you can stomach it,

01:26:56.728 --> 01:27:00.398
you should look into it.

01:27:46.070 --> 01:27:47.947
Oh, my God.

01:28:44.588 --> 01:28:47.549
Dear Judge,

01:28:47.674 --> 01:28:51.636
I recruited the best men
in Mexico for my task force.

01:28:51.721 --> 01:28:56.976
I make the selection, putting them
under a rigorous screening process.

01:28:57.059 --> 01:29:01.647
And not only physically,
but also psychologically.

01:29:01.731 --> 01:29:05.777
Judge, I'm sorry for boxes
and the paintings and things,

01:29:05.860 --> 01:29:10.031
but I have been too busy
to completely settle in here.

01:29:10.156 --> 01:29:12.825
I know you've made very good progress
with the Tijuana cartel.

01:29:12.950 --> 01:29:15.161
- Congratulations, General.
- Muchas gracias.

01:29:15.286 --> 01:29:19.457
I am confident
that before the end of the year,

01:29:19.540 --> 01:29:22.835
Juan Obregon is gonna
be taken into custody.

01:29:22.919 --> 01:29:27.673
But you must understand that it's
going to be a very difficult task...

01:29:27.799 --> 01:29:31.427
because of the corruption
in the police force.

01:29:31.552 --> 01:29:34.889
Hopefully, the exchange
of training methods and information...

01:29:34.972 --> 01:29:37.225
between our two countries will help.

01:29:37.350 --> 01:29:39.519
I hope so.

01:29:39.644 --> 01:29:43.481
On another note, General,
we were talking about supply.

01:29:43.564 --> 01:29:46.360
- Mm-hmm.
- What about demand?

01:29:46.485 --> 01:29:49.446
What are your policies
towards treatment of addiction?

01:29:49.571 --> 01:29:52.699
"Treatment of addiction."

01:29:52.783 --> 01:29:55.035
Addicts treat themselves.

01:29:55.160 --> 01:29:59.248
They overdose, and then there's
one less to worry about.

01:30:05.003 --> 01:30:09.675
What I want you to do right now
is write down five triggers...

01:30:09.758 --> 01:30:11.885
that could lead
to your relapse,

01:30:12.010 --> 01:30:14.430
that could jeopardize
your recovery.

01:30:14.513 --> 01:30:19.435
Five triggers.
Your parents, something they could say.

01:30:19.518 --> 01:30:22.396
Anything that's a trigger for you.
It varies from person to person.

01:30:22.479 --> 01:30:26.900
Some of us
have already discussed--

01:30:26.984 --> 01:30:29.069
Linda, we talked about it
the other day.

01:30:29.194 --> 01:30:31.113
I know you have trouble
with your sister,

01:30:31.196 --> 01:30:35.033
how she's always
kind of outshining you.

01:30:43.793 --> 01:30:46.629
Hey, sugarfoot,
how do you like your new home?

01:30:49.674 --> 01:30:53.636
- You got to be kidding me.
This is not what my lawyers negotiated.

01:30:53.762 --> 01:30:55.638
Please. Fuck your lawyers.

01:30:55.764 --> 01:30:58.475
You're not getting
any goddamn cappuccino or--

01:30:58.600 --> 01:31:01.478
- Biscotti.
- Yeah, you ain't getting
none of that shit either.

01:31:01.603 --> 01:31:03.646
- Pick a bed.
- Stay off the phone, Eddie.

01:31:03.772 --> 01:31:05.690
No long-distance calls, all right?

01:31:05.815 --> 01:31:08.902
- Use 1-800-CRIMINAL if you do.

01:31:17.118 --> 01:31:20.121
Mr. Ayala first came
to see me in January.

01:31:20.205 --> 01:31:23.333
That would have been 1987.

01:31:23.458 --> 01:31:26.795
He wanted to rent warehouse space
along the harbor.

01:31:26.878 --> 01:31:31.008
I didn't ask too many questions.
I am a businessman also.

01:31:31.133 --> 01:31:35.679
I was the company's secretary
from 1991 to 1994.

01:31:35.805 --> 01:31:40.017
I supposedly worked for all
six companies, but they weren't--

01:31:40.142 --> 01:31:44.355
I mean, it was just an empty office
with a desk and a telephone.

01:31:44.480 --> 01:31:47.399
I never sold anything
the whole time I was there.

01:31:47.525 --> 01:31:50.820
Sometimes people came in,
and they got paid.

01:31:50.903 --> 01:31:53.697
I-I don't really know
what they did.

01:31:53.823 --> 01:31:58.536
- Didn't Mr. Ayala
say where the money came from?
- No.

01:31:58.661 --> 01:32:03.707
-Did you ask where the money came from?
-No.

01:32:03.833 --> 01:32:05.876
Where do you think it came from?

01:32:06.001 --> 01:32:08.379
- Objection. Speculation.
- Sustained.

01:32:08.462 --> 01:32:10.881
I'll rephrase, Your Honor.

01:32:11.006 --> 01:32:16.011
Did you feel like you were engaged
in a legitimate enterprise?

01:32:17.721 --> 01:32:20.724
No, not really.

01:32:23.478 --> 01:32:25.397
Thank you.

01:32:52.215 --> 01:32:54.926
You were followed by the police,

01:32:55.051 --> 01:32:59.848
but they won't be able
to hear us over the children.

01:33:01.933 --> 01:33:05.437
I want to use a bomb.

01:33:08.774 --> 01:33:10.776
Are you kidding?

01:33:10.901 --> 01:33:13.612
Can't you just shoot him
or something?

01:33:15.239 --> 01:33:17.450
I don't really like guns.

01:33:17.575 --> 01:33:19.952
You shoot somebody in the head
two, three times...

01:33:20.077 --> 01:33:24.749
and some pinche doctor
is trying to keep him alive.

01:33:26.793 --> 01:33:29.796
When are you gonna do it?

01:33:29.921 --> 01:33:31.798
I don't know.

01:33:34.425 --> 01:33:39.055
Eduardo Ruiz is the only
real witness against Carl.

01:33:39.138 --> 01:33:41.099
Security will be very tight.

01:33:43.434 --> 01:33:48.731
- I may not be able to get to him.
- You'll be able to get to him.

01:33:48.815 --> 01:33:52.485
If they can get to
the pope and the president,
you can certainly get to him.

01:33:54.612 --> 01:33:59.158
Careful. You're starting to sound
like your husband, Mrs. Ayala.

01:34:20.305 --> 01:34:23.684
Nobody saw her leave?

01:34:23.809 --> 01:34:26.186
Hmm.

01:34:26.311 --> 01:34:28.689
No, I understand.

01:34:28.814 --> 01:34:31.358
Okay.

01:34:34.403 --> 01:34:36.864
I gotta go.

01:34:36.989 --> 01:34:39.867
I've got to go home.

01:34:39.950 --> 01:34:42.870
Did you want me to resch--

01:34:42.995 --> 01:34:45.497
Fine.

01:34:58.887 --> 01:35:02.265
What's going on? You seem nervous.

01:35:02.390 --> 01:35:04.642
- Because of Manolo.

01:35:04.726 --> 01:35:08.062
I'm afraid he'll do something foolish
and it's going to get him killed.

01:35:08.146 --> 01:35:09.647
Why?

01:35:09.731 --> 01:35:12.692
He says he's going
to sell information to the DEA.

01:35:12.776 --> 01:35:15.862
They're going to pay him
a lot of money.

01:35:18.281 --> 01:35:21.201
What could he tell the DEA?

01:35:21.659 --> 01:35:23.328
You know...

01:35:23.411 --> 01:35:25.413
about Salazar and Madrigal.

01:35:34.714 --> 01:35:36.591
Javier.

01:35:40.095 --> 01:35:42.222
Where is he right now?

01:35:43.264 --> 01:35:47.310
I don't know.
He took his passport and left.

01:35:51.774 --> 01:35:54.110
Give me a kiss.

01:35:54.193 --> 01:35:55.277
Don't tell him that I told you.

01:35:55.402 --> 01:35:57.279
No.

01:36:27.059 --> 01:36:30.813
What you want? Pot? Rock?
Hey, what you want?

01:37:19.488 --> 01:37:22.699
- Fuck!

01:37:39.175 --> 01:37:41.719
What the fuck do you want?

01:38:10.540 --> 01:38:12.416
Yeah.

01:40:27.221 --> 01:40:30.724
It has come to our attention that
Your Honor, while in private practice,

01:40:30.850 --> 01:40:33.060
previously represented
the town of Seal Beach...

01:40:33.185 --> 01:40:36.063
in their stop-work suit against
the police department of Seal Beach.

01:40:36.188 --> 01:40:38.732
We believe this disqualifies you
from hearing this case,

01:40:38.858 --> 01:40:42.778
and we, therefore, move for a temporary
suspension until it's investigated.

01:40:42.903 --> 01:40:45.030
Mr. Adler, this is
a most unusual motion.

01:40:45.156 --> 01:40:47.074
Nonetheless, Your Honor,

01:40:47.158 --> 01:40:50.411
we feel our client deserves
every fairness afforded under the law.

01:40:50.536 --> 01:40:55.541
I hope this is not in anyway designed
to delay the testimony of Eduardo Ruiz.

01:41:00.212 --> 01:41:02.882
We will recess until 9:00 a.m.
on Monday morning,

01:41:02.965 --> 01:41:07.053
and I will see counsel
in my chambers.

01:41:23.737 --> 01:41:26.114
They are coming this way.

01:41:29.534 --> 01:41:32.204
All of them are there.

01:41:32.329 --> 01:41:35.040
They are passing me now.

01:41:40.921 --> 01:41:43.882
Boy, there's a lot of them.

01:41:43.965 --> 01:41:48.804
Listen, would you mind if we
walked back to the hotel today?

01:41:48.887 --> 01:41:51.640
- Walk back?
- Yeah.

01:41:55.602 --> 01:41:57.771
They're not getting into the car.

01:41:59.273 --> 01:42:01.609
What are they doing?

01:42:01.692 --> 01:42:03.945
They're arguing or something.

01:42:06.823 --> 01:42:09.158
It's two blocks.
I could use the fresh air.

01:42:09.283 --> 01:42:11.744
I've been stuck in that piece of shit
hotel room for two weeks.

01:42:11.828 --> 01:42:14.455
I don't give a fuck.
Let's just stop standing around.

01:42:14.539 --> 01:42:16.666
- I want to walk 'cause I want to walk,
not 'cause he wants to walk.
- Let's walk.

01:42:16.791 --> 01:42:18.709
I like that.
Okay, we'll walk.

01:42:21.671 --> 01:42:23.923
They're going past me.

01:42:27.635 --> 01:42:32.140
I-I-I do not know. I think
they're going back to the courthouse.

01:42:32.223 --> 01:42:37.228
This could be the last chance
to do this! Get out of the car
and shoot him in the head!

01:42:56.415 --> 01:42:58.375
You're a fucking big man?

01:42:58.500 --> 01:43:03.755
I'm a real fucking man. I don't fucking
deal drugs to little fucking kids, you--

01:43:07.468 --> 01:43:09.011
Fucking rat.

01:43:09.136 --> 01:43:12.097
- You think you're a badass?
- I am a badass!

01:43:14.016 --> 01:43:17.644
Move, move! Get down!

01:43:25.277 --> 01:43:27.988
- Go, go, go!
We need an ambulance.
- Go, go, go.

01:43:56.893 --> 01:43:59.646
Ray. Ray! Ray!
Wait a minute, Ray!

01:44:46.944 --> 01:44:49.321
Manolito, Manolito, Manolito.

01:44:49.697 --> 01:44:51.824
What's up, Manolo?

01:44:53.826 --> 01:44:56.454
Looks like you're waiting
for someone.

01:44:56.620 --> 01:44:58.622
I'm just looking for the waitress.

01:44:59.331 --> 01:45:01.625
I'm ready to order.
Do you want anything?

01:45:01.709 --> 01:45:04.587
A fucking salad?
Something to drink?

01:45:04.670 --> 01:45:07.631
No, no. Calm down, calm down.

01:45:07.715 --> 01:45:11.719
What are you gonna have, Manolito?

01:45:14.430 --> 01:45:16.474
A steak.

01:45:18.517 --> 01:45:20.644
Well, if you like steak...

01:45:20.770 --> 01:45:23.272
we know a much better place.

01:45:23.647 --> 01:45:26.066
You come with us.

01:45:54.387 --> 01:45:57.224
Javier had nothing to do with this.

01:45:58.558 --> 01:46:01.061
It was all my idea.

01:46:04.231 --> 01:46:06.691
Punish me, not him.

01:46:11.446 --> 01:46:13.907
Do me a favor.

01:46:17.077 --> 01:46:19.496
Don't tell Ana I died like this.

01:46:21.666 --> 01:46:25.211
Tell her it was something else.

01:46:26.587 --> 01:46:29.215
Something official.

01:46:34.428 --> 01:46:36.931
Tell her I died
doing something worthy.

01:46:40.268 --> 01:46:42.478
Forgive me, Javi.

01:46:49.944 --> 01:46:52.363
Put some muscle into it.

01:46:53.448 --> 01:46:55.491
You too, Manolo.

01:47:02.999 --> 01:47:05.376
You're done.

01:47:05.460 --> 01:47:07.378
- Get out of there.
- Don't you hear?

01:47:07.462 --> 01:47:10.756
Javier, put the shovel down.

01:47:12.383 --> 01:47:15.012
Get out. Let's go.

01:47:16.513 --> 01:47:19.099
I told you it wasn't his fault.

01:47:19.183 --> 01:47:20.934
Shut up.

01:47:25.355 --> 01:47:27.524
Turn around.

01:47:43.081 --> 01:47:45.334
Let's go, Javier. It's over.

01:48:01.892 --> 01:48:05.187
Don't be alarmed, Javier.

01:48:05.313 --> 01:48:07.607
The old man works like this.

01:48:07.732 --> 01:48:10.819
We had to go
through the same thing.

01:48:12.570 --> 01:48:16.116
We had to do this
to be sure we could trust you.

01:48:16.491 --> 01:48:18.493
Now we see that we can.

01:48:18.618 --> 01:48:21.371
We are family now.

01:49:24.101 --> 01:49:26.437
Sorry about the other night.

01:49:28.397 --> 01:49:30.274
Me too.

01:51:38.489 --> 01:51:44.203
Thank you for coming down here, though I
suspect it has been a pointless journey.

01:51:44.328 --> 01:51:48.332
- Why would you say that?
- Bueno, pues, I hear these stories.

01:51:48.415 --> 01:51:51.752
Your husband in jail,
his business in chaos,

01:51:51.835 --> 01:51:54.963
various people fighting
over the scraps.

01:51:55.088 --> 01:51:58.842
My husband was a victim of an informer
in your organization, not in ours.

01:51:58.926 --> 01:52:01.553
That is not true, Mrs. Ayala.

01:52:01.678 --> 01:52:04.473
Your route has been compromised.

01:52:04.598 --> 01:52:07.976
Perhaps it is time for me to deal
with other distributors in California.

01:52:08.102 --> 01:52:10.229
- I don't think you're gonna do that.
- You don't?

01:52:10.354 --> 01:52:13.065
- No.

01:52:13.190 --> 01:52:17.903
My husband was working on something
he called the Project for the Children.

01:52:18.028 --> 01:52:23.909
- Are you aware of this?
- I don't know.
Perhaps I remember something.

01:52:27.371 --> 01:52:31.918
If you want to smuggle narcotics
in Senor Espastico Jacobo,

01:52:32.043 --> 01:52:34.254
that is nothing new, Senora.

01:52:34.379 --> 01:52:38.091
No, not in.
The doll is cocaine.

01:52:38.216 --> 01:52:42.137
High impact,
pressure-molded cocaine.

01:52:44.055 --> 01:52:47.100
It's odorless,
undetectable by the dogs.

01:52:47.225 --> 01:52:50.145
- Undetectable by anyone.

01:52:50.228 --> 01:52:52.480
I don't believe you, senora.

01:53:16.671 --> 01:53:19.382
I'm six months pregnant.

01:53:19.507 --> 01:53:21.427
I won't do it.

01:53:21.510 --> 01:53:24.847
- Then we don't have a deal.
- Yeah, right.

01:53:24.930 --> 01:53:27.349
We don't have a deal.

01:53:28.517 --> 01:53:31.979
Sorry to waste your time,
Mr. Obregon.

01:53:33.606 --> 01:53:35.524
Okay.

01:53:35.608 --> 01:53:37.526
Okay, okay.

01:53:46.786 --> 01:53:50.164
- That's good coke.
- It should be. It's yours.

01:53:52.041 --> 01:53:53.918
I want our debt forgiven,

01:53:54.043 --> 01:53:58.506
I want to be the exclusive
distributor of Obregon brothers'
cocaine in the United States,

01:53:58.631 --> 01:54:03.385
and I want the principal witness against
my husband, Eduardo Ruiz, killed.

01:54:10.309 --> 01:54:13.271
Have you told the complete truth
during this interview?

01:54:15.482 --> 01:54:18.235
Yes.

01:54:19.402 --> 01:54:22.030
- Alex?
- Solid.

01:54:22.155 --> 01:54:24.574
- That's good shit, Javier.
- You know, Javier,

01:54:24.658 --> 01:54:27.202
they dump those cell phones
every 24 hours.

01:54:27.285 --> 01:54:30.872
Yes, but I have
a contact at MexTel...

01:54:30.997 --> 01:54:35.210
who can get me
his new E.S.N. in 12 hours.

01:54:35.293 --> 01:54:37.254
That's good to know.

01:54:41.341 --> 01:54:44.261
So, now that you have
what you want,

01:54:44.344 --> 01:54:47.556
let's talk about how
I get what I want.

01:54:47.681 --> 01:54:49.891
Oh, you don't have
to worry about that.

01:54:50.016 --> 01:54:52.727
You're not gonna have
any problems there.

01:54:52.853 --> 01:54:57.232
Yeah, but first let's talk
about what precautions you're
taking to protect yourself.

01:54:57.315 --> 01:55:01.278
You worry about getting me
what I want.

01:55:01.403 --> 01:55:03.780
I'll worry about myself.

01:55:08.453 --> 01:55:12.915
Oye, Javier,
you should feel good about this.

01:55:16.210 --> 01:55:18.629
I feel like a traitor.

01:56:44.800 --> 01:56:49.012
Helena Ayala just left Club Platinum,
the Obregon brothers' place in Tijuana.

01:56:49.138 --> 01:56:51.182
- Yeah?
- She got stopped at the border.

01:56:51.307 --> 01:56:55.728
She was clean,
and she's back in San Diego now.

01:56:55.812 --> 01:56:57.730
Okay.

01:57:07.991 --> 01:57:11.703
- Hello?
- Robert, it's Jeff Sheridan.

01:57:11.828 --> 01:57:14.038
- D-Did I wake you? I'm sorry.
- No, it's okay.

01:57:14.164 --> 01:57:16.207
General Salazar has been arrested.

01:57:16.332 --> 01:57:18.751
It turns out he has been working
for Porfirio Madrigal...

01:57:18.835 --> 01:57:20.879
and the Juarez cartel
the entire time.

01:57:21.004 --> 01:57:24.215
That is why he was trying to push
the Obregons out of Tijuana...

01:57:24.340 --> 01:57:26.551
- so he and Madrigal could move in.
- What?

01:57:26.676 --> 01:57:29.679
I thought Madrigal was dead.
I thought that had been verified.

01:57:29.762 --> 01:57:33.057
Apparently not. It is a shitstorm here,

01:57:33.183 --> 01:57:37.228
but the D.E.A. supplied the information
and was part of the sting.

01:57:37.353 --> 01:57:40.774
So, maybe we can spin this a little,
but I don't know what to tell people.

01:57:40.857 --> 01:57:44.069
-So, when are you coming back?
-I'll try to get there as soon as I can.

01:57:44.195 --> 01:57:46.405
- Yeah, okay, but--
- Robert.

01:57:46.530 --> 01:57:50.951
Robert? Robert?

01:57:51.035 --> 01:57:53.245
I gotta call you back.

01:57:53.370 --> 01:57:55.289
- What--

01:57:59.877 --> 01:58:04.924
- My Leica's missing.
- She got the video camera too.

01:58:05.049 --> 01:58:08.093
At least we know she's still alive.
Where are you going?

01:58:08.219 --> 01:58:12.264
Pawn shops open in an hour. Ten minutes
after that, she'll be at her dealer.

01:58:12.389 --> 01:58:15.935
If I can find him,
I should be able to find her.

01:58:25.653 --> 01:58:29.782
Although
ser and estar both mean "to be,"

01:58:29.907 --> 01:58:33.786
they have very specific uses.

01:58:33.869 --> 01:58:36.832
May I help you, sir?

01:58:41.670 --> 01:58:43.463
Excuse me!

01:58:43.588 --> 01:58:47.008
Seth has to be excused.
He's going on a field trip.

01:58:53.098 --> 01:58:56.810
I can't believe you brought
my daughter to this place.

01:58:58.603 --> 01:59:03.316
Whoa, whoa. Why don't you just
back the fuck up, man?

01:59:03.442 --> 01:59:05.485
"To this place"?

01:59:05.610 --> 01:59:07.821
What is that shit?

01:59:07.946 --> 01:59:10.866
Okay, right now, all over
this great nation of ours,

01:59:10.949 --> 01:59:13.660
100,000 white people from the suburbs
are cruising around downtown...

01:59:13.785 --> 01:59:17.497
asking every black person,
"You got any drugs? You know
where I can score some drugs?"

01:59:17.622 --> 01:59:21.543
Think about the effect that has
on the psyche of a black person,
on their possibilities.

01:59:21.626 --> 01:59:25.672
I-- God, I guarantee you,
you bring 100,000 black people
into your neighborhood,

01:59:25.755 --> 01:59:30.011
and they're asking every white
person, "You got any drugs?
Know where I can score some?"

01:59:30.136 --> 01:59:34.348
Within a day, everyone would be
selling--your friends, their kids.

01:59:34.474 --> 01:59:38.186
Here's why: It's an unbeatable market
force, man. It's a 300% markup value.

01:59:38.311 --> 01:59:41.147
You can go out on the street
and make $500 in two hours,

01:59:41.230 --> 01:59:43.232
come back and do whatever you want
with the rest of your day.

01:59:43.316 --> 01:59:47.904
You're telling me that white people
would still be going to law school?

02:00:12.678 --> 02:00:15.890
- What do you want?
- I'm looking for my daughter.

02:00:15.973 --> 02:00:17.892
Caroline.

02:00:17.975 --> 02:00:20.437
She's been here.

02:00:20.521 --> 02:00:22.564
This is a business, man.
Why don't you get the fuck out ofhere?

02:00:22.689 --> 02:00:26.610
I need to find my daughter, all right?
I'll pay you.

02:00:27.694 --> 02:00:30.906
All right.
Okay. Hold on.

02:00:34.034 --> 02:00:38.247
Who in the fuck do you think you are?
Where the fuck do you think you are?

02:00:38.372 --> 02:00:43.418
- Why the fuck shouldn't I just
put your ass in a Dumpster?
- I got money.

02:00:43.544 --> 02:00:46.088
- I got money!
- I got $1,000 in my wallet.

02:00:46.213 --> 02:00:50.259
- It's for you.
- If I want your money, man,
I will take your money.

02:00:52.553 --> 02:00:55.097
Just tell me
where my daughter is.

02:00:55.222 --> 02:00:57.683
Please? Please?

02:01:03.230 --> 02:01:05.441
Don't do that shit again.

02:01:11.906 --> 02:01:16.619
Look, Jesus, man, I'm telling you,
don't do this vigilante thing.

02:01:16.744 --> 02:01:19.789
Either the cops are gonna find her,
or she's gonna call you.

02:01:19.914 --> 02:01:21.833
Okay?

02:01:21.916 --> 02:01:23.835
I promise.

02:01:52.238 --> 02:01:54.157
Ana.

02:01:55.700 --> 02:01:58.536
If Manolo hadn't done what he did...

02:01:59.454 --> 02:02:03.833
they wouldn't have been able
to get Salazar and Madrigal.

02:02:08.422 --> 02:02:11.008
He did something really good.

02:02:14.053 --> 02:02:17.932
What's more, he did
something important for Tijuana.

02:02:19.475 --> 02:02:21.894
I would like to believe you.

02:02:29.527 --> 02:02:32.988
You don't have to believe me...

02:02:35.116 --> 02:02:37.243
because it's the truth.

02:02:38.494 --> 02:02:40.913
The simple truth.

02:02:57.180 --> 02:02:59.891
Tomorrow I'm going
to burn his clothes.

02:03:47.731 --> 02:03:50.902
I know she's in there.
Just let me talk to her.

02:03:50.985 --> 02:03:53.780
Look, I know she's in there, man!

02:03:53.905 --> 02:03:56.449
No, I fucking know she's in there!

02:04:00.244 --> 02:04:02.413
Jesus Christ!

02:04:02.497 --> 02:04:05.166
I-I haven't touched her.

02:04:11.088 --> 02:04:14.300
You get the fuck
out of here right now.

02:04:27.271 --> 02:04:29.190
Hi.

02:04:35.780 --> 02:04:37.990
Hi, Daddy.

02:04:41.160 --> 02:04:43.330
Hi, sweetheart.

02:05:16.822 --> 02:05:20.033
Hey, good morning, Eddie.

02:05:20.159 --> 02:05:22.202
- Good morning.
- Big day.

02:05:23.662 --> 02:05:28.208
You're a star.

02:05:28.333 --> 02:05:30.752
Why don't you go take a shower, man?
You smell.

02:05:32.838 --> 02:05:36.509
- Who is it?
- It's the Mafia.

02:05:36.593 --> 02:05:39.929
- I've got his breakfast.
- Coming.

02:05:43.683 --> 02:05:45.602
- So who's this going to?
- Over here.

02:05:53.359 --> 02:05:56.321
- Ooh.
- Fuck off.

02:05:56.446 --> 02:06:00.658
- Relax, Eddie.
- Yeah, where has the love gone?
Good-bye.

02:06:02.535 --> 02:06:04.579
You know, you're gonna be testifying
for about ten days.

02:06:04.704 --> 02:06:06.915
We could just decide
to stop feeding your ass.

02:06:07.040 --> 02:06:10.960
You expect me to be grateful
for spending the rest of my life
looking over my shoulder?

02:06:11.044 --> 02:06:14.756
Wow, that's--
that's heavy, Eddie.

02:06:17.550 --> 02:06:21.262
Can't you for one second imagine
that none of this had happened,
that my drugs had gone through?

02:06:21.387 --> 02:06:23.306
What would be the harm?

02:06:23.389 --> 02:06:25.600
Huh? What would be the harm?

02:06:25.725 --> 02:06:28.437
A few people get high
who are getting high anyway.

02:06:28.562 --> 02:06:31.607
Your partner's still alive.

02:06:31.732 --> 02:06:35.152
We don't have to have
breakfast together.

02:06:35.236 --> 02:06:37.279
Don't you see this means nothing?

02:06:37.404 --> 02:06:39.615
Your whole life is pointless.

02:06:40.908 --> 02:06:43.327
You're really breaking my heart.

02:06:45.246 --> 02:06:50.793
- The worst part about you, Monty--
- "Monty"?

02:06:50.918 --> 02:06:52.837
The worst part about you, Monty,

02:06:52.920 --> 02:06:56.257
is you realize the futility of what
you're doing, and you do it anyway.

02:06:56.340 --> 02:06:59.135
Wish you could see
how transparent you are.

02:06:59.260 --> 02:07:01.387
This food tastes like shit.

02:07:01.512 --> 02:07:05.307
So, take your stank ass
and go get a shower already.

02:07:07.268 --> 02:07:09.186
Let me tell you something.

02:07:09.270 --> 02:07:12.189
You only got to me because you
were tipped off by the Juarez cartel...

02:07:12.273 --> 02:07:14.191
who's trying to break into Tijuana.

02:07:14.275 --> 02:07:17.695
- You are helping them. Uh-huh.
- Mmm.

02:07:17.778 --> 02:07:20.824
So, remember, you work
for a drug dealer too, Monty.

02:07:22.200 --> 02:07:24.202
- Fuck me.

02:07:24.286 --> 02:07:27.205
- Who is it?
- Breakfast.

02:07:29.791 --> 02:07:31.710
Hurry up.
It's getting cold.

02:07:36.423 --> 02:07:38.341
Okay. One second.

02:07:39.593 --> 02:07:42.179
- Get the fuck down!
- Hey, hey, hey, hey, hey!

02:07:42.262 --> 02:07:45.849
- Get down! Get the fuck down!
- Hey, hey, I'm on your side!

02:07:45.932 --> 02:07:49.102
- What the fuck?
- Oh, shit. Call an ambulance.

02:07:49.227 --> 02:07:52.189
- Call an ambulance! Fuck!
- Palms up.
Spread your damn hands out.

02:07:52.314 --> 02:07:55.358
- Shit! Eddie!

02:07:57.903 --> 02:07:59.988
Hold on.

02:08:00.071 --> 02:08:03.283
Oh, shit!
Hurry up with that ambulance!

02:08:03.408 --> 02:08:06.036
Shit. Hold on. Hold on.

